citation: Proclamation under the Electricity Supply Industry Act 1995 (Tas)
text:
Proclamation under the Electricity Supply Industry Act 1995

I, the Administrator in and over the State of Tasmania and its Dependencies in the Commonwealth of Australia, acting with the advice of the Executive Council, by this my proclamation made under section 2 of the Electricity Supply Industry Act 1995 fix 20 July 2005 as the day on which Division 3 of Part 3 of that Act commences.

11 July 2005

E. C. CRAWFORD

Administrator

By His Excellency's Command,

P. A. LENNON

Treasurer

Displayed and numbered in accordance with the Rules Publication Act 1953.

Notified in the Gazette on 20 July 2005

This proclamation is administered in the Department of Treasury and Finance.
